            <SimpleData name="Additional_notes">This is the list of all sensors reporting to the AOOS Portal are at ~33m on this data feed, though there maybe other sensors on this mooring as well not reported on the portal. AOOS Portal link: https://portal.aoos.org/#metadata/123829/station/data</SimpleData>
