            <SimpleData name="Station_Deployment">2018-06-30 00:00:00</SimpleData>
            <SimpleData name="Currently_Operational">O - Operated intermittantly April 2025 - August 19 2025 Only, offline rest of the year.</SimpleData>
            <SimpleData name="Platform_Funder">IOOS OTT, BIA, AOOS, NOAA-OAP</SimpleData>
            <SimpleData name="RA_Funded">Yp</SimpleData>
            <SimpleData name="Platform_Operator">This information is currently being revised: POC: Darcy Dugan, dugan@aoos.org; Oregon State University and Alutiiq Pride Shellfish Hatchery</SimpleData>
