            <SimpleData name="Additional_notes">Data In portal starts June 30, 2018. AOOS used to support BoL OnM through Hakai and provided support to Alutiiq Pride Shell Fish Hatcher in 2018-19 directly. Stopped reporting real time November 2020. Briefly operated in Real time in March - April 2024. Hakai is no longer managing the data from this BOL. APMI staff worked directly with Tetra Tech (previously called Axiom Data Science) to get the RT Data Feeds back up and running in 2025. Managed to operate and report RT data April 2025 - August 2025, but not since. Not sure why DO is not included in the suite for BOLs. AOOS has been supporting this BOL in 2021-2025. Not Reporting at time of RA Asset Inv update (as of Jan 12 2026)</SimpleData>
            <SimpleData name="file">AOOS.xlsx</SimpleData>
          </SchemaData>
        </ExtendedData>
