            <SimpleData name="Additional_notes">AOOS contracted with ASTRA LLC to prepare portable code for Axiom to convert the GNSS data to water level. Water level data currently on the portal are releative to the GPS antenna. We need to adjust the data to a MLLW / Datum  and resolve  many drop outs in the datastream (probably due to satellite signal issues, but some due to plotting algorithm). Water level reported with respect to the antenna height. Not ready for WMO/CMAN ID</SimpleData>
