            <SimpleData name="Additional_notes"><![CDATA[This station has had multiple previous deployments between Nov 16, 2016 and Jun 28, 2021. On June 8, 2022, a field team traveled to Kotzebue to replace the sensor with a Stillwater Technologies iGageX and re-establish the site. Keith Horen computed tidal datums using the Alaska Today Datum Portal, which are available in the linked Station Definition Form.On Nov. 3, 2022, ortho and station datum heights in the metadata file were updated. Data from 6/02/2022 to 11/3/2022 were reloaded. Data are also found on NOAA APRFC website:  https://water.weather.gov/ahps2/hydrograph.php?wfo=pafg2&gage=kzta2]]></SimpleData>
